## Recommended Wordlists (from SecLists)
/usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/common.txt          — fast, common dirs

/usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/directory-list-2.3-medium.txt  — thorough

/usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/raft-large-files.txt  — file discovery

/usr/share/seclists/Discovery/DNS/subdomains-top1million-5000.txt  — DNS

/usr/share/seclists/Discovery/DNS/subdomains-top1million-20000.txt — DNS thorough

Install SecLists:
```bash
sudo apt install seclists
# or
git clone https://github.com/danielmiessler/SecLists /usr/share/seclists
```

