## Gobuster vs ffuf vs dirb

| Tool | Speed | Features | Best for |
|------|-------|----------|---------|
| Gobuster | Fast | DNS, vhost, dir | General use, CTFs |
| ffuf | Very fast | Highly customisable | Advanced fuzzing |
| dirb | Slow | Simple | Quick checks |

