## Key Terms

| Term | Meaning |
|------|---------|
| Dir brute forcing | Guessing hidden paths on a web server |
| Subdomain | A prefix of a domain, e.g. `admin.target.com` |
| Vhost | Multiple websites sharing one IP |
| SecLists | Collection of wordlists for security testing |
| 403 Forbidden | Resource exists but access is blocked |
| Extension fuzzing | Appending `.php`, `.bak` etc. to find hidden files |
